node.text: Currently itching for another adventure✈️ This is the Rio Grande River in Big Bend National Park - the rocks you see behind me are actually Mexico!🌎 I’m open to suggestions of where I should head to next to do something really cool outdoors!🤔

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Captain Katherine Salom on August 24, 2021 tagging @officialmauijim, @berkleyfishing, @yamahaoutboards, @favoriterodsusa, @blazer_boats, @eyestrikefishing, @lagunamadre, @garminmarine, and @koastalkustoms. May be an image of 1 person and body of water.

node.text: Put the smackdown on some trout this morning!🎣 Decided to try some of our Fall fishing spots and glad to see that the fishing patterns are changing - the trout are moving up and I’m excited!🙌🏻 Got around 30 trout in the boat and then the surprise chunky drum (2nd pic)🔥 Caught them all on @eyestrikefishing jig heads using @matrixshad_docksidetv and @berkleyfishing baits!👏🏻

node.text: I won’t lie to you - definitely had a little trauma when I unhooked some catfish today and almost threw my @danco_pliers overboard when the catfish started flopping lmao 😅🎣 but felt great to get out on the water for a little while!🔥 Caught some redfish and tried to even out the 17 different tan lines on my body 🥵🤦🏼‍♀️
